div.h4: In this type of assignment you have to draw a route
div.h5:
• Click on the road to show the way. Red dots will appear, and show the way.
• Click on the road in the front, if you want many red dots to appear.
• Click on the red dots to delete a part of the route.
• You cannot walk the same route twice.
div.h6: Try to draw a road to the big circus tent. It starts at the red arrow at the bottom.
